01:42.728 --> 01:45.316
No, I-I'm not coming.

01:45.317 --> 01:47.027
I don't want to be a
part of the discussion

01:47.028 --> 01:48.572
about future leadership.

01:48.573 --> 01:50.451
Look, Cal and Eddie can hash it out.

01:51.996 --> 01:53.582
Hold on, someone's at the door.

01:53.583 --> 01:56.003
Who is it?

01:56.004 --> 01:58.926
Felicia, I'm gonna
have to call you back.

02:03.895 --> 02:06.065
- Remember me?
- No.

02:06.066 --> 02:07.610
I'm one of the people you blackmailed.

02:07.611 --> 02:09.698
I lost everything! I tried to kill you.

02:09.699 --> 02:10.824
I tried to run you off the road,

02:10.826 --> 02:12.035
but that wouldn't help.

02:12.036 --> 02:15.041
I wish I could make amends, believe me.

02:15.042 --> 02:16.962
Know that I live with what I did to you.

02:19.677 --> 02:21.304
No. Please.

02:21.305 --> 02:23.016
Live with this.

02:34.373 --> 02:37.245
I know that there is confusion.

02:38.846 --> 02:42.764
I know there's fear and sadness.

02:42.765 --> 02:46.813
But Steve, he asked me to return...

02:46.814 --> 02:48.859
to serve...

02:48.860 --> 02:53.119
to bring hope to a broken movement.

02:54.539 --> 02:59.046
I tried to silence the call,
but it was just too...

03:03.055 --> 03:04.601
Earthquake!

03:38.334 --> 03:41.297
We have to go.

03:41.298 --> 03:43.301
We have to go!

03:43.302 --> 03:44.554
Everybody out!

03:44.555 --> 03:46.223
No, no, no, it's safer here.

03:46.224 --> 03:47.602
No, we have to get out!

03:47.603 --> 03:48.854
Get out of the building!

03:48.855 --> 03:50.649
Everybody out!

03:53.238 --> 03:54.491
Get out!

03:59.418 --> 04:01.086
Anybody else in there?

04:04.260 --> 04:06.098
Hey. We have to go.

04:07.309 --> 04:09.854
We have to go.

04:15.367 --> 04:17.827
- What are we running for?
- I don't know.

04:17.829 --> 04:19.248
- We have to go.
- No, I can't.

04:19.249 --> 04:20.961
It's okay. We have to...

04:23.467 --> 04:25.051
- Dad! Dad!
- No, don't...

04:25.052 --> 04:28.015
Come on! Come on. Come on.

04:28.016 --> 04:29.353
Come on.

06:10.221 --> 06:11.890
What authorities are calling

06:11.891 --> 06:14.395
a freak earthquake caused
a gas-line explosion

06:14.396 --> 06:16.148
at the New York Meyerism Center.

06:16.149 --> 06:17.526
The group's leader, Eddie Lane,

06:17.527 --> 06:19.322
emerged from the flames unharmed.

06:19.323 --> 06:22.453
Meyerist miracle or hoax?

06:39.279 --> 06:42.493
It begins.

